# Blog posts (Markdown with YAML frontmatter)
#
# Place .md files here for blog content.
# Files are rendered via the /blog/:slug route.
#
# Example: welcome.md
#
# ---
# title: Welcome to Naked Pineapple
# description: Introducing our brand and mission
# date: 2026-01-24
# author: Naked Pineapple Team
# tags: [announcement, brand]
# featured_image: /images/blog/welcome.jpg
# ---
#
# # Welcome to Naked Pineapple
#
# Content here...
#
# Frontmatter fields:
# - title (required): Post title
# - description (required): Meta description
# - date (required): Publication date (YYYY-MM-DD)
# - author (optional): Author name
# - tags (optional): Array of tags
# - featured_image (optional): Hero image URL
# - draft (optional): Set to true to hide from listing
